name: steve hsu
description: physicist, startup founder, blogger, dad
tweets:
@lu_sichu Note, it's top few pct ability in the *general population*, not within the *STEM* population. 

The STEM population is already highly selected and comes from top ~10% already, so the 10x refers to maybe top 1 in 3 or 5 engineers, scientists, etc. even at the BS level.
